Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架機體是!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的人們的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 那聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 露易絲!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!? 為什麼沙慈的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲… 難道在MS裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈! 你在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈! 在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道在 Gundam裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲 難道你現在是A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:46.06,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說 能把我的夢想托付給沙慈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:49.74,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到宇宙去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:52.88,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:56.28,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 你會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:01.61,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 讓我的夢想實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.89,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈… 我們約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此路不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋我者死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是增援嗎
