Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大佐的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
