Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓縮粒子 填充完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音
