Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體量子化了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam居然隱藏了我所不知的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有些驚慌的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你這臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 沒有Gadessa怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人MS部隊 開始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 終止炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機 保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那那傢伙 打下多少敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多10架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放鬆 我們還有破壞衛星武器的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 我知道你擔心著父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是麻煩你操作Karel維修托密勒和Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經將運輸艦護送至安全區域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 你媽媽安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 我趕緊去忙維修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有如此性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來啊 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·庫洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去露易絲那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到沙慈的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天行者那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和殺害爸爸媽媽的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 他也是組織的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他身邊就是沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是一夥的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙推進Gundam那近乎異常的機體性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機體究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 伊恩的傷勢如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過10天左右就可以恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·庫洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了露易絲的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來她在MS裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還喊了我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 她會在A-LAWS裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為憎恨Gundam啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲的父母 是被Gundam殺掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你們的錯 露易絲加入了A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一直在這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要與命運抗爭的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將露易絲·哈勒維 從A-LAWS奪回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去… 戰鬥?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的那麼重視她的話 應該能夠做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是讓我去殺人麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去把她奪回來的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那裡狡辯了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的話就會有人受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲也是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你自己而戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們這些人才不一樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別相提並論!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種癖好可不怎麼好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不小心聽到了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你還真的很笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那個小子直說清楚不就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他說「戰鬥由我來擔下」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你去說服什麼的也好」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把她從A-LAWS奪回來」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不一定會順利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你不是已經滿腦子想著要這麼做了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要消除過去的罪惡麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:08.97,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}發信人：露易絲·哈勒維\N　地址：RH.SK>>ΦFINEΣWAY\N　標題：寫給沙慈\N\N在宇宙等我哦。\N馬上就會追上你了。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那張照片上 是您夫人麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2個月之前還是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被捲入KATARON的反聯邦恐怖襲擊死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在這裡麼 准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齊寧大尉被晉陞成為中佐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰鬥途中 聽到了聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在和敵人通話麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在敵人之中有准尉認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽上去是很親密的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙是我家人的仇人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是給這個世界招致不幸的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很嬌嫩的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像是駕駛員應該有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該在這A-LAWS裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:15:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們竟然處於人類的下風!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是裡本斯告訴過我TWIN DRIVE的性能的話!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯·阿爾馬克?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林格 聽到了麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00的奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 希林格和迪拜因竟然也被投入戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 連裡本斯也不清楚TWIN DRIVE的性能麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:26.71,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}裡切拉王國 軍事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星兵器又發射了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 朝裡切拉的軍事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要削弱中東的軍力麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地附近 應該有一個百萬人規模的難民營…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 也被牽連了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將無罪的人們的生命奪取
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在說什麼世界統一!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那種做法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府覺得能迎來真正的和平嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在消逝而去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁言令?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在說什麼 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS使用的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用太陽能發電
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從衛星軌道發射的大功率射線攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種大規模殺傷性武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦大統領下達的特令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能無視
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的士兵們全都目擊了現場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言論馬上會傳開的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對A-LAWS的做法大呼不滿的人也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拜託你擔任監察一職
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將禁言令執行徹底
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令麼? 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 軍方的決定不能變更
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要服從軍紀…麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和王留美取得聯繫了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有應答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是想要衛星兵器的情報的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛 衛星兵器向地面發射了第二彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間磨磨蹭蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪向全員傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密號外部裝甲的補修作業完成之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻以TRANS-AM最大加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊軌道環上的敵軍衛星兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的補修在加速航行時也繼續進行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 拜託了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這個宙域的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和露易絲就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事要拜託你 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼? 什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰之前一定會修好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰友他們都平安無事麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛斯洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微被人家拜託了點事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去見她 見露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能呆在A-LAWS裡面!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明是不相關的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在這些地方才很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只讓想打的傢伙隨便打好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要取回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些時光…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種轉身無視現實的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會成為無意識的惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致這樣的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪去他們性命的人 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你那愚蠢的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又 要做相同的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim Arios Seravee的各太陽爐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和托勒密號動力部的直接連接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM 開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密號 最大出力!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…露易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過10分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙戰艦就能到達衛星兵器的攻擊可能地點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰鬥 就會決定一切啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信同志們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星兵器 以光學攝像頭捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2艦隊的狀況怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就會到達指定地點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達之後 兩支艦隊利用時間差立刻開始進行導彈攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長! 衛星兵器動了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮 炮身竟… 轉到上方!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 這個角度 第2艦隊嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第 第2艦隊 半數被消滅!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三發 發射了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 進行分析!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兵器 也能向宇宙射擊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.09,0:23:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的宇宙艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.16,0:23:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫雜種…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是聯邦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.55,0:23:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革者的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星兵器理應破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者執行決死任務
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Memento-Mori攻略戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.08,0:24:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是 Gundam機師的神髓
